"-Z macro-backtrace for more info)\n"
"help: consider cloning the value if the performance cost is acceptable\n"
"  |\n"
"3 |     let s2 = s1.clone();\n"
"  |                ++++++++\n"
"\n"
"For more information about this error, try `rustc --explain E0382`.\n"
