#: src/ch09-03-to-panic-or-not-to-panic.md:254
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Then, we implement an associated function named `new` on `Guess` that "
"creates instances of `Guess` values. The `new` function is defined to have "
"one parameter named `value` of type `i32` and to return a `Guess`. The code "
"in the body of the `new` function tests `value` to make sure it’s between 1 "
