#~ "the kinds of   errors that might occur and what conditions might cause "
#~ "those errors to be   returned can be helpful to callers so they can write "
#~ "code to handle the   different kinds of errors in different ways. * "
#~ "**Safety**: If the function is `unsafe` to call (we discuss unsafety in   "
